div.p: Got it you want your portfolio hero section (the second screenshot) to look visually and structurally like ChaiCodes landing page (the first screenshot).
That design has the following defining features:

li.p: Dark gradient background with subtle honeycomb pattern.
Large, bold heading with mixed font weights (similar to Consistency and Community).
Subheading with emphasized keywords in a glowing accent color.
Clean two-column layout: text-heavy left side and image on the right, with balanced spacing.
A smaller top badge (Trusted by style).
Slight brown/orange glow behind the image.

div.p: Heres your updated Hero.tsx rewritten to match that design language closely:
